{"id":"docs","title":"Angular 文档简介","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"introduction-to-the-angular-docs\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e7cnkwgxl0ebxhofcg954759v\">Angular 文档简介<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#introduction-to-the-angular-docs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cruh429zga8xgk660sgk6uj0f\">Angular 是一个应用设计框架与开发平台，旨在创建高效而精致的单页面应用。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dlc4cz723sunv28oknpfr16gg\">这份 Angular 文档会帮助你学习和使用 Angular 框架与开发平台，从你的第一个应用开始，一直到优化复杂的企业级单页面应用。\n这些教程和指南中都包含可下载的范例，以加速你的学习。</p>\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n  <a href=\"tutorial/first-app\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Work through a full tutorial\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"412em5ac5un2jynxs26cn1qwx\">构建你的第一个 Angular 应用</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"78jn4r9eoj8wf9mbh3npojs0k\">完成一个完整的教程，创建你的第一个应用程序。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"83xx69b4cb3gn93xp2atsnja9\">应用教程</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/what-is-angular\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular Platform Overview\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3ah1qj7vi1n0g9z2zoyfp8h3z\">什么是 Angular</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"41ki0yzw19np9j0765jlkhsew\">对 Angular 平台进行一次高层概览。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"do1196v6lj343c1vj0vy2tgl2\">平台概览</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/architecture\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular Concepts\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3lsloce94hj49azg6z1nohu73\">深入探索</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a7pnmd3uyvw5ql9gmfx4hvak5\">学习 Angular 应用的更多知识及架构特性</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7578hxgxtlup3f3iuhimhupk5\">Angular 概念简介</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/setup-local\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular Local Environment Setup\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"as8wq9decz3tva4qfpiyftnlq\">搭建开发环境</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"af8e8jtu8rer1gamokwt3cb5x\">使用 Angular CLI 搭建本地开发环境。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"chzefi040i3qk5by22qrkg645\">本地搭建</p>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"assumptions\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"60gfjoc3stm6be15s3zzobvyz\">基本假设<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#assumptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"em4g6ljic98pb60pmncsfyyi1\">本文档假设你已经熟悉了 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML\" title=\"Learn HTML\">HTML</a>，<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps\" title=\"Learn CSS\">CSS</a>，<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/A_re-introduction_to_JavaScript\" title=\"Learn JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> 和来自 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Language_Resources\" title=\"Latest JavaScript standards\">最新标准</a> 的一些知识，比如  <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes\" title=\"ES2015 Classes\">类</a> 和 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/import\" title=\"ES2015 Modules\">模块</a>。\n下列代码范例都是用最新版本的 <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/\" title=\"TypeScript\">TypeScript</a> 写的。\n大多数 Angular 代码都只能用最新的 JavaScript 编写，它会用 <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/classes.html\" title=\"TypeScript Types\">类型</a> 实现依赖注入，还会用<a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/decorators.html\" title=\"Decorators\">装饰器</a>来提供元数据。</p>\n<h2 id=\"feedback\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"babdupp5y5gbzfr3ih6tdgh1y\">反馈<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#feedback\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_We = NO -->\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"avjkgova99kcm1yl4gr5snqym\">我们希望听到你的声音！<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/new/choose\" title=\"Angular GitHub repository new issue form\">欢迎报告问题或为文档的未来提交建议</a>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3njlgn9m73ddm3vj8g9nxwqhy\">请到 GitHub 上的仓库中创建 <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/pulls\" title=\"Angular Github pull requests\">Pull Requests</a> 来为 Angular 文档做出贡献。\n<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md\" title=\"贡献者指南\">贡献者指南</a>将会帮助你更好的为社区做贡献。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cox4lswgc0xongkl5gvm8b5ow\">我们的社区提倡相互尊重、相互支持。\n参阅<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/code-of-conduct/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md\" title=\"contributor code of conduct\">社区行为规范</a>。</p>\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_We = YES -->\n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/docs-style-guide\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/localizing-angular\n - guide/updating\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - docs#assumptions\n - docs#feedback\n - docs#introduction-to-the-angular-docs\n - guide/architecture\n - guide/setup-local\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - tutorial/first-app\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/A_re-introduction_to_JavaScript\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Language_Resources\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/import\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/new/choose\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/pulls\n - https://github.com/angular/code-of-conduct/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md\n - https://www.typescriptlang.org/\n - https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/classes.html\n - https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/decorators.html\n-->"}